        <title>Extra Learning Opportunities</title>
        <contents>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;img src="@@PLUGINFILE@@/58056366_thumbnail.jpg" width="120" height="120" alt="" style="margin: 5px; float: right;" /&gt;Tech Tips&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;Tech Tips are distributed throughout the unit and provide advice about strategies for dealing with the unexpected, as well as ideas for solutions to issues raised in technology.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;img src="@@PLUGINFILE@@/68886853_thumbnail.jpg" width="100" height="105" alt="" style="float: right; margin: 5px;" /&gt;To Go Deeper&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;Also distributed throughout the unit are readings for those who want to delve deeper into the specific topic. Most of the resources can be found at a public or academic library.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;If you'd like to delve deeper into topics while you are learning, establish (or activate) an account with your library and find out how to get journal articles online and how to get academic books.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;&lt;img src="@@PLUGINFILE@@/58056366_thumbnail.jpg" width="120" height="120" alt="" style="margin: 5px;" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;Tech Tip&lt;/summary&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Here is your first tech tip. There are many links in this unit, and as is always the case with links, they may become broken. If so, try to use a browser to search for the site, using a name from the link, the title, or other description. If you can’t find it, don’t worry and move on.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/details&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</contents>
